<s> Or is there already a requirement to provide an easy way to move the "focus" or start of search to the beginning or end of the document.  </s>
<s> (3) Should provide distinct alerts for the three situations listed; the user should be able to easily tell whether they have searched all the content, or whether they merely reached the end of the document and now need to wrap to the beginning.  </s>
<s> (4) There are a lot of additional variations that could be included as priority 3. For example, should add the ability to search backwards through content, possibly as a priority 3 checkpoint.  </s>
