<s> [I make this proposal only for checkpoint 7.3 and not for checkpoints in Guideline 12.] Issue 413 (Second Last Call): Checkpoint 6.2: Does this only apply to content?  </s>
<s> Yes, this applies only to content.  </s>
<s> There has been no change to the document because it was considered that the label in the document "Checkpoints for content" was sufficient, but given other changes to the document subsequently, I think this requires an additional (editorial) clarification to the checkpoint.  </s>
<s> (I will write a proposal to the Working Group.) I'll wait to see your proposed modifications, but I strongly favor writing all checkpoints so that their meanings are not significantly changed when quoted out of context.  </s>
