<s> /IJ2 Issue 414 (Second Last Call): Checkpoint 7.3: Need stronger min requirements There has been no increase in the minimal navigation requirements for what is now checkpoint 9.2: "9.2 Allow the user to move the content focus to any enabled element in the viewport.  </s>
<s> If the author has not specified a navigation order, allow at least forward sequential navigation to each element, in document order.  </s>
<s> The user agent may also include disabled elements in the navigation order."  </s>
